{"tid":2073812,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"習大大同柒婆簡直係天作之合！造就黃色經濟圈！","createTime":"2020-06-21T15:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T23:42:14.000Z","uid":127575,"like":600,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"47b074e36cc24f9834d8a284c345ee70027d76ac","tid":2073812,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:09:23.000Z","msg":"一年前未有社會事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多港豬一到放假返去深圳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食海底撈／喜茶／地溝油垃圾食品<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n振興深圳經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰時根本就唔知咩叫黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知........心急如焚習大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> + 好勝心強柒婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無啦啦搞逃犯條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n引發史上最嚴重民憤仲要不斷火水救火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到越嚟越好多人唔信支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喚醒唔少港豬見識到支那要有幾閪就有幾閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入境支那仲要無啦啦搞查人身分證查人手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚇走晒後生仔唔再去支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未有中国病毒之前<br />\n一連串社會事件<br />\n已經間接衝擊深圳經濟<br />\n之後依家雪上加霜<br />\n支那病毒搞到好多深圳熱門地方店舖收撚晒皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再加上有黃色經濟圈越做越大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多香港人寧願支持本地黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未來應該唔會再去支那振興紅色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一年變化真係好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住黃色經濟圈越來越強<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望大家巴絲真係唔好放棄黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"de1b00000139a1fa924ef2601dfabacf702bf8dd","tid":2073812,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:10:50.000Z","msg":"哭撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">藍店</div>"},{"pid":"e2831cb0baafd8f81473a586e391d1cd6f10d82e","tid":2073812,"uid":41545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"What about施生同人民日報 大公文匯日日足奏既功能"},{"pid":"1933544885fa8fa96ff4b9e054d7f0e170bf1714","tid":2073812,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b11a477b9fc48f663a208739a3e94a895c85548","tid":2073812,"uid":38982,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"唔止咁, 呢兩條檬柄唔止將黃色經濟圈係香港普及, 仲將色經濟圈既威力擴展到全世界!! 而家由美國帶領全世界唔同中國做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37cc77464d0f8042a8bec96893c9379b63690500","tid":2073812,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b11a477b9fc48f663a208739a3e94a895c85548","tid":2073812,"uid":38982,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"唔止咁, 呢兩條檬柄唔止將黃色經濟圈係香港普及, 仲將色經濟圈既威力擴展到全世界!! 而家由美國帶領全世界唔同中國做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:18:19.000Z","msg":"加速主義冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望繼續火